    <title class="- topic/title "><ph class="- topic/ph topic/title-wrapper ">How to create a new account in Steam ? </ph></title>
    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc ">Here im going to show you how to create a new account by using the Steam
        client.</shortdesc>
    <body class="- topic/body ">
        <p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Prerequisites</b> : You need to download  the Steam client first before you can create
            a new account.Here is the link from where you can dowload it. <xref class="- topic/xref " format="html" href="https://store.steampowered.com/" scope="external"/><ol class="- topic/ol " id="unique_2_Connect_42_ol_dhc_ts3_5pb" nd:nd-id="ol_dhc_ts3_5pb">
                <li class="- topic/li ">Open you'r steam client that looks like this :  <p class="- topic/p "><image class="- topic/image " href="file:/C:/Users/UserPC/Desktop/Dita_pic/Steam_client.png" id="unique_2_Connect_42_image_tsn_htx_xpb" nd:nd-id="image_tsn_htx_xpb" placement="inline"/></p></li>
                <li class="- topic/li ">Click the "Create a New Account..." button from the Steam login page. <p class="- topic/p "><image class="- topic/image " href="file:/C:/Users/UserPC/Desktop/Dita_pic/Create_a_new_account.png" id="unique_2_Connect_42_image_cc4_ltx_xpb" nd:nd-id="image_cc4_ltx_xpb" placement="inline"/></p></li>
                <li class="- topic/li "> After you click "Create a New Account" then it will show you a window with
                    information that needs to be filled in order to create a new account.<p class="- topic/p "><image class="- topic/image " href="file:/C:/Users/UserPC/Desktop/Dita_pic/Instructions.png" id="unique_2_Connect_42_image_bl1_f5x_xpb" nd:nd-id="image_bl1_f5x_xpb" placement="inline"/></p><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Result: </b>After you finish writing down the information
                        that is needed, the end result should look like this.</p><p class="- topic/p "><image class="- topic/image " href="file:/C:/Users/UserPC/Desktop/Dita_pic/Created_account.png" id="unique_2_Connect_42_image_idr_lvx_xpb" nd:nd-id="image_idr_lvx_xpb" placement="inline"/></p></li>
            </ol></p>
    </body>
</topic><topic break-before="true" is-chapter="true" class="- topic/topic " id="unique_3" topicrefclass="- map/topicref " nd:nd-id="how_can_you_use_all_the_functionalities_of_steam_requirements" oid="how_can_you_use_all_the_functionalities_of_steam_requirements" specializations="@props/deliveryTarget">
    <title class="- topic/title "><ph class="- topic/ph topic/title-wrapper ">How can you use all the functionalities of Steam(requirements) ?</ph></title>
    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc ">Here im going to show you how to unlock all the functionalities that Steam can offer. </shortdesc>
    <body class="- topic/body ">
        <p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Prerequisites :</b> You need to download the Steam client first before you can use
            it's functionalities. Here is the link from where you can dowload it. <xref class="- topic/xref " format="html" href="https://store.steampowered.com/" scope="external"/></p>
        <p class="- topic/p ">You will need to spend at least <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">$5.00 USD</b> within the Steam store.</p>
        <p class="- topic/p ">Some examples of purchases that grant access to these features are:</p>
        <ul class="- topic/ul " id="unique_3_Connect_42_ul_mlr_kt3_5pb" nd:nd-id="ul_mlr_kt3_5pb">
            <li class="- topic/li ">Adding the equivalent of $5 USD or more to your Steam Wallet.</li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">Purchasing game(s) that are equal to $5 USD or more from the Steam store.</li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">Adding a Steam Wallet card that is equal to $5 USD or more to your Steam
                account<p class="- topic/p "/>Each Steam purchase total will be tracked in USD. If your Steam store's
                currency isn't in USD, it will be tracked and converted to USD automatically using
                daily exchange rates.</li>
        </ul>
    </body>
</topic><topic break-before="true" is-chapter="true" class="- topic/topic " id="unique_4" topicrefclass="- map/topicref " nd:nd-id="how_to_sent_a_friend_request" oid="how_to_sent_a_friend_request" specializations="@props/deliveryTarget">
    <title class="- topic/title "><ph class="- topic/ph topic/title-wrapper ">How to sent a friend request ?</ph></title>
    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc "> Here im going to show you how to sent a friend request.</shortdesc>
    <body class="- topic/body ">
        <p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Prerequisites :</b> You need to download the Steam client first before you can sent a
            friend request. Here is the link from where you can dowload it.<xref class="- topic/xref " format="html" href="https://store.steampowered.com/" scope="external"/></p>
        <ol class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">Open the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Steam</b> client.<p class="- topic/p "><image class="- topic/image " href="file:/C:/Users/UserPC/Desktop/Dita_pic/Steam_start.png" id="unique_4_Connect_42_image_vkp_zyx_xpb" nd:nd-id="image_vkp_zyx_xpb" placement="inline"/></p></li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">After you open the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Steam</b> client, you will see at the bottom of your right
                screen the button <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">FRIENDS &amp; CHAT</b>. Click it.<p class="- topic/p "><image class="- topic/image " href="file:/C:/Users/UserPC/Desktop/Dita_pic/Starter_firend_screen.png" id="unique_4_Connect_42_image_hjs_y1y_xpb" nd:nd-id="image_hjs_y1y_xpb" placement="inline"/></p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">Then it will open a new window.After that you can click the button <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">"Add a
                    friend"</b>.<p class="- topic/p "><image class="- topic/image " href="file:/C:/Users/UserPC/Desktop/Dita_pic/friend_list_add.png" id="unique_4_Connect_42_image_lys_xby_xpb" nd:nd-id="image_lys_xby_xpb" placement="inline"/></p></li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">After you click <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">"Add a friend "</b> button, it will appear a new tab with your
                    <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">code </b>and a space to write you'r friends <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">code </b>to add them.
                        <p class="- topic/p "><image class="- topic/image " href="file:/C:/Users/UserPC/Desktop/Dita_pic/Friend_Code_circle.png" id="unique_4_Connect_42_image_oqc_f5z_xpb" nd:nd-id="image_oqc_f5z_xpb" placement="inline"/></p></li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">After you write down you'r friend's code then press the button <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">"Enter" </b>from
                your keyboard. </li>
        </ol>
        <p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Result:</b>They'll get a notification that you've sent a friend request. When they
            accept the invite, you'll be added to each other's Friends List.</p>
    </body>
</topic><topic break-before="true" is-chapter="true" class="- topic/topic " id="unique_5" topicrefclass="- map/topicref " nd:nd-id="how_to_search_your_type_of_game" oid="how_to_search_your_type_of_game" specializations="@props/deliveryTarget">
    <title class="- topic/title "><ph class="- topic/ph topic/title-wrapper ">How to search your type of game ?</ph></title>
    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc ">Here im going to show you how to search you'r type of game.</shortdesc>
    <body class="- topic/body ">
        <p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Prerequisites :</b> You need to download the Steam client first before you can search
            for you'r type of game. Here is the link from where you can dowload it.<xref class="- topic/xref " format="html" href="https://store.steampowered.com/" scope="external"/></p>
        <p class="- topic/p ">
            <ol class="- topic/ol " id="unique_5_Connect_42_ol_c2z_2v3_5pb" nd:nd-id="ol_c2z_2v3_5pb">
                <li class="- topic/li ">Open your <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Steam</b> application <p class="- topic/p "><image class="- topic/image " href="file:/C:/Users/UserPC/Desktop/Dita_pic/Steam_start.png" id="unique_5_Connect_42_image_l5m_rvz_xpb" nd:nd-id="image_l5m_rvz_xpb" placement="inline"/></p></li>
                <li class="- topic/li ">Then you click the button <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">"Categories"</b>. Its location is next to <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">"New
                        &amp; Noteworthy"</b> and <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">"Points Shop"</b>
                    <p class="- topic/p "><image class="- topic/image " href="file:/C:/Users/UserPC/Desktop/Dita_pic/Categories.png" id="unique_5_Connect_42_image_fr5_511_ypb" nd:nd-id="image_fr5_511_ypb" placement="inline"/></p></li>
                <li class="- topic/li ">After you write down you'r friend's <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">code</b> then press the button <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">"Enter"
                    </b>from your keyboard. <p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Result:  </b><image class="- topic/image " href="file:/C:/Users/UserPC/Desktop/Dita_pic/game_inspection.png" id="unique_5_Connect_42_image_iyc_qc1_ypb" nd:nd-id="image_iyc_qc1_ypb" placement="inline"/></p></li>
            </ol>
        </p>
    </body>
</topic><topic break-before="true" is-chapter="true" class="- topic/topic " id="unique_6" topicrefclass="- map/topicref " nd:nd-id="how_to_purchase_a_game" oid="how_to_purchase_a_game" specializations="@props/deliveryTarget">
    <title class="- topic/title "><ph class="- topic/ph topic/title-wrapper ">How to purchase a game ?</ph></title>
    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc "> Here im going to show you how to purchase you'r favorite games.</shortdesc>
    <body class="- topic/body ">
        <p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Prerequisites :</b> You need to download the Steam client first before you can
            purchase you'r favorite game. Here is the link from where you can dowload it.<xref class="- topic/xref " format="html" href="https://store.steampowered.com/" scope="external"/></p>
        <p class="- topic/p ">
            <ol class="- topic/ol " id="unique_6_Connect_42_ol_udn_rdh_wpb" nd:nd-id="ol_udn_rdh_wpb">
                <li class="- topic/li ">Start you'r <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Steam </b>application from you'r executable file.<p class="- topic/p "><image class="- topic/image " href="file:/C:/Users/UserPC/Desktop/Dita_pic/Steam_client.png" id="unique_6_Connect_42_image_sqj_5d1_ypb" nd:nd-id="image_sqj_5d1_ypb" placement="inline"/></p></li>
                <li class="- topic/li ">Then go to the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">"search tab"</b> and add the title of the game that you want
                    to search.<p class="- topic/p "><image class="- topic/image " href="file:/C:/Users/UserPC/Desktop/Dita_pic/Steam_start_search_game.png" id="unique_6_Connect_42_image_xq4_121_ypb" nd:nd-id="image_xq4_121_ypb" placement="inline"/></p></li>
                <li class="- topic/li ">After you add you'r game title It will show you the result of your
                            search.<p class="- topic/p "><image class="- topic/image " href="file:/C:/Users/UserPC/Desktop/Dita_pic/Gmae_result.png" id="unique_6_Connect_42_image_wwv_cf1_ypb" nd:nd-id="image_wwv_cf1_ypb" placement="inline"/></p></li>
                <li class="- topic/li ">Then you can browse and click the "<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">product<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">"</b></b> that you wish to
                    inspect.It will show you a detail screen of the game. <p class="- topic/p "><image class="- topic/image " href="file:/C:/Users/UserPC/Desktop/Dita_pic/game_inspection.png" id="unique_6_Connect_42_image_w4k_kf1_ypb" nd:nd-id="image_w4k_kf1_ypb" placement="inline"/></p></li>
                <li class="- topic/li "> After you decide that you want to purchase this <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">"product" </b>you can click
                    the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">"Add to Cart" </b>button.<p class="- topic/p "><image class="- topic/image " href="file:/C:/Users/UserPC/Desktop/Dita_pic/game_inspection_Add_to_cart.png" id="unique_6_Connect_42_image_yqd_vf1_ypb" nd:nd-id="image_yqd_vf1_ypb" placement="inline"/></p></li>
                <li class="- topic/li ">Then it will ask you if you'r purchasing it for <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">"youtself"</b> or for a
                        <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">"friend"</b><p class="- topic/p "><image class="- topic/image " href="file:/C:/Users/UserPC/Desktop/Dita_pic/yourself_or_friend.png" id="unique_6_Connect_42_image_ag3_xf1_ypb" nd:nd-id="image_ag3_xf1_ypb" placement="inline"/></p></li>
                <li class="- topic/li ">After you choose one of thoese options and then it will show you the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">"payment
                        information"</b>.<p class="- topic/p "><image class="- topic/image " href="file:/C:/Users/UserPC/Desktop/Dita_pic/payment_information.png" id="unique_6_Connect_42_image_qml_xg1_ypb" nd:nd-id="image_qml_xg1_ypb" placement="inline"/></p></li>
                <li class="- topic/li ">And finally after you fill the information needed, click the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">"Continue"
                    </b>button to complete the purchase.<p class="- topic/p "><image class="- topic/image " href="file:/C:/Users/UserPC/Desktop/Dita_pic/payment_information_coplete.png" id="unique_6_Connect_42_image_i2d_bh1_ypb" nd:nd-id="image_i2d_bh1_ypb" placement="inline"/></p><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Result : </b>After you completed all
                        the steps, the purchase should be complete.</p></li>
            </ol>
        </p>
    </body>
